    div.legal-container
      h1 Flora Safety Standards & Child Protection
      p At Flora, we are committed to maintaining a safe, mature, and respectful environment. Because our community is built specifically for adults (21+) who share distinct lifestyle values, we employ a "Safety-by-Design" philosophy. This means protection is integrated into the architecture of the app from the very first interaction.

      h2 1. Age Integrity & Identity Verification
      p Flora is strictly for users aged 21 and older. We do not allow minors on the platform under any circumstances.
      ul
        li #[strong Mandatory Verification:] To ensure the integrity of our community, every user must complete a secure identity verification process before they can access the Discovery feed or interact with others.
        li #[strong Zero Document Storage:] We prioritize your privacy by utilizing industry-leading third-party verification. Flora does not store copies of your legal ID documents on our local servers; we only receive a confirmation that you are a real person over the age of 21.

      h2 2. Proactive Content Moderation
      p We take an active role in monitoring the content shared within our ecosystem to prevent the spread of harmful or illegal imagery.
      ul
        li #[strong AI-Powered Image Scanning:] Every image uploaded to Flora is automatically analyzed by advanced Computer Vision technology. This system is trained to identify and block prohibited content, including nudity, violence, and any imagery involving minors, before it ever becomes visible to the community.
        li #[strong Real-time Protection:] Our automated safeguards operate 24/7, ensuring that the platform remains a sanctuary for intentional connection.

      h2 3. Community Reporting & Enforcement
      p Safety is a shared responsibility. We empower our users with robust tools to help keep the Flora community clean and accountable.
      ul
        li #[strong Direct Reporting:] Every profile and chat thread includes a reporting feature. If a user encounters behavior that violates our community standards, they can flag it immediately for review.
        li #[strong Rapid Response:] Our moderation team reviews reported content with urgency. Accounts found to be in violation of our safety policies—especially those involving harassment or attempts to bypass age restrictions—are subject to permanent bans.
        li #[strong Accountability:] Because every account is tied to a verified identity, we can effectively prevent bad actors from creating multiple accounts or returning to the platform after a ban.

      h2 4. Child Safety Statement (CSAM Policy)
      p Flora has a zero-tolerance policy toward child sexual abuse material (CSAM).
      ul
        li #[strong Detection & Removal:] Any attempt to upload or distribute CSAM will result in an immediate and permanent account termination.
        li #[strong Legal Reporting:] In accordance with federal and international law, Flora will report any instances of suspected child exploitation to the National Center for Missing & Exploited Children (NCMEC) and cooperate fully with law enforcement agencies.

      h2 Legal References
      p For more detailed information regarding your data, privacy, and community guidelines, please review our official policies:
